      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S PICKLE (7) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on her slick win the start prior, getting around this track over 520m in 29.80. Has the ability and looks hard to top. NANGAR ZENA (4) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only a neck (30.07) behind Grace Ile at this track. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in three starts. Ready to find winning form. CANYA SHOTFIRE (8) drawn the outside box and could get a clear run. Was below best last time when 7th and beaten 23 lengths at Q Lakeside (27.37). Has never missed the frame here at the trip including zero wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Deserves plenty of respect. PRODUCER (1) has not raced here but still warrants respect.",
